  "title": "Stacker",
  "description": "Change the stack size of all items!",
  "body": "# Stacker\nMinecraft mod to change the stack size of all items. For Fabric 1.17, 1.18, 1.18.2, and 1.19!\n<br><br>\n![Stacker Mod Cover Image](https://imgur.com/C0I2Z2p.png)\n<br><br>\nThis mod has a config that defaults to 64. Change it to be whatever you like (below int_max), but I do not recommend anything too far over 1 Billion (No support will be given for stacks larger than 1,073,741,823).\n<br><br>\nRequires Stacc API and Cloth Config API. Stacc API is an embedded library, so don't worry about downloading it. I recommend installing with Mod Menu (for in-game access to the configs), but it is not needed to run.\n",
